        <updating/>
        <source>doSaveToDoWagon(_wodtl : CM_WodToDoWagon input) : Boolean updating;
/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
28 Dec 2022	navcs2	ChangeRequest 56835:[56836] EUP - VAS Truck Work Order
14 March 2023  navhl20	ChangeRequest 56840:[54265] EUP - [Framework] - VAS Work Order Maintenance Screen
